claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: CONSORT flow diagram showing screening and enrollment of participants in Year 1 and Year 2 of an influenza vaccine study, with arms IIV4, ccIIV4, and RIV4 (Flublok Quadrivalent) and counts of participants re-randomized or excluded. The figure is a participant enrollment flowchart and does not present any information on antigenic matching of Flublok to WHO- or FDA-selected strains, therefore it does not support the claim Note: Image clarity is sufficient to confirm absence of antigenic match data
